      "raw_text": "of the Great Northern system they\nappear to be bound to secrecy and\nwill give out no information. This\nnew division will go into effect July\n1. One thing is certain and that is\nthat a general shakeup of officials is\ncontemplated.\n\n\nw. d. Scott, superintendent, and F.\n8. Elliot, assistant superintendent,\nboth of the Cascade division, passed\nthrough the city yesterday without\ntheir private car, bound for Kalispell,\nwhich lends strength to the rumor\nthat a shakeup is imminent.\n\n\n1t has been given out that w. Will\nlerton, now trainmaster of the Cas-\ncade division. will be made assistant\nsuperintendent Of the new division."
